[2026-07-11T15:20:58.858Z] [INFO] 
[2026-07-11T15:20:58.858Z] [INFO] This project leverages AI-driven development with human oversight. Follow these practices:
[2026-07-11T15:20:58.858Z] [INFO] 
[2026-07-11T15:20:58.858Z] [INFO] ### Development Workflow
[2026-07-11T15:20:58.858Z] [INFO] 
[2026-07-11T15:20:58.858Z] [INFO] 1. **Issue Creation** - Humans create issues with clear requirements
[2026-07-11T15:20:58.858Z] [INFO] 2. **AI Processing** - Hive Mind analyzes and proposes solutions
