[2026-07-11T15:20:58.858Z] [INFO] ### Code Standards
[2026-07-11T15:20:58.858Z] [INFO] 
[2026-07-11T15:20:58.858Z] [INFO] - **TypeScript/JavaScript**: Strict typing required
[2026-07-11T15:20:58.858Z] [INFO] - **File Size**: Maximum 1000 lines per file
[2026-07-11T15:20:58.858Z] [INFO] - **Testing**: 100% test coverage for critical paths
[2026-07-11T15:20:58.858Z] [INFO] - **Documentation**: Machine-readable, token-efficient
