[2026-07-11T15:25:44.951Z] [STDOUT] Fixes #2045

## Summary

- lower the built-in `HIVE_MIND_DISK_THRESHOLD` default from `0.8` to `0.65` for both the structured disk threshold and legacy `DISK_THRESHOLD` alias
- preserve the `enqueue` strategy and all environment-variable overrides
- update regression coverage for the ratio and derived 65% display threshold

## Verification

- `node tests/queue-config.test.mjs`
- `node tests/test-issue-1981-disk-defaults.mjs`
- `node tests/test-telegram-solve-queue.mjs`

The full lint/default test commands could not run in this workspace because its Node version is `20.20.2`, while the project requires Node `>=24`; npm installed packages but did not create executable shims (`eslint: not found`).
