{"blocked_by":0,"total_blocked_by":0,"blocking":0,"total_blocking":0},"body":"## Request\n\nChange the default disk queue-admission threshold from **0.8 → 0.65**.\n\n`HIVE_MIND_DISK_THRESHOLD` currently defaults to `0.8` (set in #1981, raised from the older `0.9`). In practice `0.8` still leaves too little headroom on disk-constrained isolation hosts — tasks continue to be launched at 80% used and then die at ~100% while a `--isolation docker` task expands images/scratch. Operators keep having to manually lower it to `0.65` in their env to get a safe margin.\n\n## Where\n\n`src/queue-config.lib.mjs`:\n\n```js\n// line ~250 (thresholds.disk)\ndisk: getThresholdConfig('disk', 'HIVE_MIND_DISK_THRESHOLD', 'HIVE_MIND_DISK_STRATEGY', 0.8, 'enqueue'),\n// line ~266 (legacy flat DISK_THRESHOLD)\nDISK_THRESHOLD: getThresholdConfig('disk', 'HIVE_MIND_DISK_THRESHOLD', 'HIVE_MIND_DISK_STRATEGY', 0.8, 'enqueue').value,\n```\n\nBoth `0.8` default literals should become `0.65`.\n\n## Why 0.65\n\n- `--isolation docker` tasks need substantial free disk for image layers + per-task scratch; starting at 80% used routinely fills the host before a task completes.\n- `0.65` is the value operators already fall back to manually (e.g. the hive-control-center deployment), so making it the default removes a required override.\n- The `enqueue` strategy is unchanged — tasks wait rather than being rejected, so a lower threshold just means the bot backs off earlier and resumes once disk frees up.\n\n## Scope\n\n- Update the two default literals above.\n- Update any doc/comment referencing the `0.8` default (e.g. the `Issue #1981` comment block).\n- No env-var/API change — operators can still override via `HIVE_MIND_DISK_THRESHOLD` or `HIVE_MIND_QUEUE_CONFIG`.\n\nFollow-up to #1981.\n","closed_by":null,"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/link-assistant/hive-mind/issues/2045/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/link-assistant/hive-mind/issues/2045/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":null,"pinned_comment":null}
